  {
    "type": "help",
    "helpvalue": "<h2>II - Information Technology (IT) Security Assessment</h2>"
  },
  {
    "type": "fieldset",
    "items": [
      {
        "type": "help",
        "helpvalue": "<p>In order to avoid any misuse or inadvertent disclosure of information that could indirectly identify research participants or disclose their private data to unauthorized individuals, the Data Access Oversight Committee requires that you follow basic IT security practices. If you make local copies of the consortium research data, you must effectively minimize the risk that this information might be disclosed to individuals who have not agreed to the consortium’s privacy protection conditions.</p>"
      },
      {
        "type": "help",
        "helpvalue": "<p><strong>You must agree to the following practices and procedures in order to have access to the consortium research data:</strong></p>"
      },
      "aggreementA",
      "aggreementB",
      "aggreementC",
      "aggreementD",
      "aggreementE",
      "aggreementF"
    ]
  }
